To install this framework, You should update the config file included on 'Application/Config/core.php' and 'Application/Config/db.php'.

1. Setup your Home Directory URL.
define('BASE_URL', 'YOUR-PROJECT-DIRECTORY-URL');

2. Setup your Database Information
private static $host_name = 'YOUR-DATABASE-HOME';
private static $db_name = 'YOUR-DATABASE-NAME';
private static $db_user_name = 'YOUR-DATABASE-USERNAME';
private static $db_password = 'YOUR-DATABASE-PASSWORD';

3. Import `stage4cancercommunity.sql` file on your Database. You may find this file on home Directory.

4. Please put 1 if it's your root directory otherwise leave it 2 on line #26 at router.php (Optional)

All Done.
Enjoy!